statement.p:
Use the Law of Cosines to prove:

            1 + \cos A \amp = \dfrac{(a + b + c)(-a + b + C)}{2bc}
            1 - \cos A \amp = \dfrac{(a - b + c)(-a + b + C)}{2bc}
